'''Balleny Basin''' ({{Coord|67|S|170|E|source:GNIS|display=inline,title}}) is a minor [[Oceanic basin|undersea basin]], almost an appendage to the [[Southeast Pacific Basin]]. It was named in association with the [[Balleny Islands]] and the name approved by the [[Advisory Committee on Undersea Features]] February 1972.

